  "remarks": "\nListed pursuant to paragraph 7(c) of UN Security Council Resolution 1591 (2005). As a General in the RSF and Commander of West Darfur he is an individual who impedes the peace process, constitutes a threat to stability in Darfur and the region and has committed violations of international humanitarian or human rights law or other atrocities.\n",
